Package: darwinkit
Title: R Interface to the DarwinKit Darwin Core Validator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hakai Institute", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "info@hakai.org")
Description: Build Darwin Core / OBIS validation configs from data frames with
    pipeable verbs and validate them against the DarwinKit engine (the dwkt
    binary).
URL: https://github.com/HakaiInstitute/DarwinKit
BugReports: https://github.com/HakaiInstitute/DarwinKit/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    nanoparquet,
    jsonlite,
    processx,
    utils,
    yaml
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr,
    pkgdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
